GET api.traefik.me/api/blogs/ed4cc555-2d96-48ad-94e0-1c27ae44014c/comments

### Get a comment by id
GET api.traefik.me/api/blogs/ed4cc555-2d96-48ad-94e0-1c27ae44014c/comments/30e9f88c-5d13-420e-a49d-0b73f303d0d9

### Create a comment
POST api.traefik.me/api/blogs/ed4cc555-2d96-48ad-94e0-1c27ae44014c/comments

{
